import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import 'react-loader-spinner/dist/loader/css/react-spinner-loader.css'
import App from './App'
import './index.css'

export const Context = createContext(null)

ReactDOM.render(
  <ContextProvider>
    <App />
  </ContextProvider>,
  document.getElementById('root')
)
